    "intro": "Jude refuses to leave the reader as a spectator. The letter ends with imperatives — build, pray, keep, wait, show mercy — and a doxology that promises God will do what Jude has commanded. Answer the following questions specifically. Name the teaching, the relationship, the doubt, the choice. Don't generalize.",
